{"tid":2079934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Google取消儲存新用家搜尋紀錄","createTime":"2020-06-26T06:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T06:19:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4dfe71e0b28c46753a330a4718a79bfe83d40b2b","tid":2079934,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:07:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200626/6PTT5SEVSP6SXZTPF6XHNEF3SU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200626%2F6PTT5SEVSP6SXZTPF6XHNEF3SU%2F&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2StTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=64a27d97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200626%2F6PTT5SEVSP6SXZTPF6XHNEF3SU%2F&h=20b5345e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200626/6PTT5SEVSP6SXZTPF6XHNEF3SU/</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle取消儲存新用家搜尋紀錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FKyBlIhD-qpOtnoGeOkUgA_Yhik=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AFY4GYXQJPCDGG2UI6RU76AL5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFKyBlIhD-qpOtnoGeOkUgA_Yhik%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAFY4GYXQJPCDGG2UI6RU76AL5E.jpg&h=5afec325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n15億Google賬戶須手動改設定。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\nGoogle前日宣佈不會儲存新用戶完整的搜尋紀錄，應用程式和網頁上的搜尋紀錄、定位紀錄、語音服務紀錄和YouTube活動紀錄將保留3至18個月後自動刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n15億舊賬戶需手動設定<br />\n<br />\nGoogle原先會把有關資料自動永久保存，稱是為了向用戶提供個人化服務。去年首次提議推出自動刪除的設定，讓用戶可自行決定數據儲存的到期日，使關注私隱的用戶可不再長年留下網絡足迹。<br />\n<br />\n新用戶今後預設的自動刪除設定不適用於Gmail和Google相簿。另外用戶亦可更輕易在使用搜尋器、地圖和YouTube的手機應用程式時轉用無痕模式，只需長按個人資料圖片便可。<br />\n<br />\n不過現時全球擁有Google賬戶的15億人就需手動更改設定。<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n在搜尋頁面上搜尋「Google私隱檢查」等字眼，就可查看其私隱和安全設定。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle過去數月面對消費<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n集過多用戶數據，承諾改善。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社"},{"pid":"d435fe986cd33e7fa9fb6dcba94dd7ac1d5efe00","tid":2079934,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"因為儲存過長既紀錄成本高, marketing效益底?"},{"pid":"775fcfbbdbd1be5f0e2e332c1ecc0838cfc0312c","tid":2079934,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:11:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82a3ad806e6f6021481f371e939973db5c6a7964","tid":2079934,"uid":68483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"775fcfbbdbd1be5f0e2e332c1ecc0838cfc0312c","tid":2079934,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d435fe986cd33e7fa9fb6dcba94dd7ac1d5efe00","tid":2079934,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"因為儲存過長既紀錄成本高, marketing效益底?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:11:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:18:01.000Z","msg":"近半年太多PR公司開新帳號洗版<br />\n不論歐洲黑人平權同香港都多左好多新acc<br />\n啲big data完全錯曬"},{"pid":"c00fce2dd1e9bc23c873687bfe67d09fcefbda56","tid":2079934,"uid":68483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82a3ad806e6f6021481f371e939973db5c6a7964","tid":2079934,"uid":68483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"775fcfbbdbd1be5f0e2e332c1ecc0838cfc0312c","tid":2079934,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d435fe986cd33e7fa9fb6dcba94dd7ac1d5efe00","tid":2079934,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"因為儲存過長既紀錄成本高, marketing效益底?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:11:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:18:01.000Z","msg":"近半年太多PR公司開新帳號洗版<br />\n不論歐洲黑人平權同香港都多左好多新acc<br />\n啲big data完全錯曬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:19:24.000Z","msg":"仲要計埋支那同印度鳩刷view，其實google今年啲data冇咩參考價值"}]}